OL,3,C'No butter without guns': Lord
OL,4,CRobertson warns UK is not ready for
OL,5,CRussia threat
OL,7,FFormer Labour defence secretary George
OL,8,FRobertson is worried. He is worried
OL,9,Fthat we are not taking the threat from
OL,10,FRussia seriously enough.
OL,12,FAnd he knows what he is talking about,
OL,13,Fbecause George - now Lord - Robertson
OL,14,Fwas the lead author of last year's
OL,15,FSecurity and Defence Review.
OL,17,FHe is also a former UK Defence
OL,18,FSecretary and former Secretary General
OL,19,Fof Nato.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
