OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777327868
OL,3,C'No butter without guns': Lord
OL,4,CRobertson warns UK is not ready for
OL,5,CRussia threat
OL,7,FLord Robertson is worried that the
OL,8,Fgovernment is not ramping up defence
OL,9,Fspending quickly enough, given the
OL,10,Fscale of the threat from Russia; "It
OL,11,Fwould be horrible to think it would
OL,12,Ftake an actual crisis, an actual
OL,13,Fattack on the United Kingdom before we
OL,14,Fwoke up to the kind of threats that
OL,15,Fare facing us," he told parliament's
OL,16,FNational Security Strategy Committee
OL,17,Ftoday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
