PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777327868
OL,3,C'No butter without guns': Lord
OL,4,CRobertson warns UK is not ready for
OL,5,CRussia threat
OL,7,FThe problem is how to pay for it when
OL,8,Fbudgets are so tight, and the public
OL,9,Fexpects a certain level of spending on
OL,10,Fother priorities. This is the 'guns
OL,11,Fversus butter' argument, and Robertson
OL,12,Fis scathing about it.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
