PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777327868
OL,3,C'No butter without guns': Lord
OL,4,CRobertson warns UK is not ready for
OL,5,CRussia threat
OL,7,F"There will be no butter if we don't
OL,8,Fhave guns," he says. "If you've got a
OL,9,Fwar, it costs a lot of money. We
OL,10,Ffinished paying for the Second World
OL,11,FWar in 2016.
OL,13,F"You know that's a war that we won...
OL,14,Fso it's a much more expensive
OL,15,Fproposition than deterrence is."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
