PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777327868
OL,3,C'No butter without guns': Lord
OL,4,CRobertson warns UK is not ready for
OL,5,CRussia threat
OL,7,FAs Robertson sees it, there is an
OL,8,Furgent need for a national
OL,9,Fconversation about these priorities,
OL,10,Fabout whether we can afford to spend
OL,11,Ffive times more on welfare than on
OL,12,Fdefence at a time when even the prime
OL,13,Fminister has warned we could be at war
OL,14,Fwith Russia by the end of the decade.
OL,16,FWhy is this not taking place?
OL,17,FRobertson recently accused the Prime
OL,18,FMinister of "corrosive complacency"
OL,19,Fabout defence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
