PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777327868
OL,3,C'No butter without guns': Lord
OL,4,CRobertson warns UK is not ready for
OL,5,CRussia threat
OL,7,FToday he was more diplomatic, saying,
OL,8,Fwith the merest hint of a rueful
OL,9,Fsmile, "It may well be that other
OL,10,Fthings are preoccupying the mind of
OL,11,Fthe prime minister and the secretary
OL,12,Fof state for defence, and that is
OL,13,Fpostponing it, but it's regrettable
OL,14,Fnonetheless."
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
